name: Wisanggeni
description:
The Prince of Fire of Poison. Wisanggeni is the strongest son of Arjuna. The ancient God forbids him and Antasena to fight in Bharatayuddha. Both warriors then stay in the God Realm, reaching 'moksa'. 

-He might be able to travel between universes, for example, that certain apocalyptic kids.
